          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
  An <html:strong>affine scheme</html:strong> is a <fr:link href="/forest/algm-000L/" title="locally ringed space" uri="https://trebor-huang.github.io/forest/algm-000L/" display-uri="algm-000L" type="local">locally ringed space</fr:link> of the form <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\operatorname {Spec}(R)]]></fr:tex> for some commutative ring <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
